subject: Reappointment of a full-time member of the Parole Board of Canada
precis: Reappointment of Terry D. Hancock of Ottawa, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Parole Board of Canada, to hold office during good behaviour for a period of five years, and her designation as full-time member of the Appeal Division of the Parole Board of Canada.
